metadata.title: Transcend USB 3.1 SDHC/SDXC/ microSDHC/SDXC Card Reader, TS-RDF5R (Pink)
features: Superspeed USB 3.0 interface; backwards compatible with USB 2.0
Supports SDHC (UHS-I), SDXC (UHS-I), Micro SD, microSDHC (UHS-I), and Microsoft (UHS-I)
Led card insertion and data transfer activity indicator
Ideal for transferring high-resolution images and video recordings
Supports SD and security functions - USB powered
description: Engineered to deliver Super fast data transfer speeds, The Rdf5 USB 3.0 card reader features a SuperSpeed USB 3.0 interface and support for next-generation Ultra High Speed SDHC/SDXC and microSDHC/SDXC cards. Capable of being plugged directly into the USB port on any desktop or notebook computer, The Ultra compact Rdf5 offers effortless file sharing in any situation.
